description:
Ignition is a PC game released in 1997 by Virgin Interactive. It features miniature cars, much like Death Rally.


Just re-discovered this olde Win95 game in a cupboard .

When installing in XP use the default location C:  GAMES  IGNITION

DO NOT (when prompted) install the olde version of directx .

XP Iso mounting software included (or download from http://www.softpedia.com/get/CD-DVD-Tools/Virtual-CD-DVD-Rom/Virtual-CDROM-Control-Panel.shtml )




